condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IA2(a) | Description :The Recipient shall establish, and thereafter maintain at all timesduring Project implementation, a Project coordination unit within MEF, with composition, terms of reference and resourcessatisfactory to the AssociationNot later than three months after effectiveness date | Due Date :23-Jun-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IA2(b) | Description :The PCU shall at all times be comprised of qualified and experiencedpersonnel in adequate numbers, and to this end, the Recipient shall recruit inter alia: (i) Project coordinator, Procurement Spec.,FM Spec., & Accountant; (ii) Infrastructure Spec., M&E Spec., Community Mobilization & Conflict Prevention Spec., & SafeguardsSpec., all with qualifications, experience, and ToR | Due Date :23-Jul-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IA3(a) | Description :The Recipient shall establish, and thereafter maintain at all timesduring Project implementation, up to three regional Project implementation units (“RPIU”) in selected regions, and withcomposition, terms of reference and resources satisfactory to the Association | Due Date :23-Sep-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section ID1 | Description :The Recipient shall adopt, in accordance with terms of referenceacceptable to the Association and, a Project Implementation Manual(“PIM”), containing detailed arrangements and procedures for:institutional coordination, Project budgeting, disbursement & financial management, procurement, M&E reporting and communication,and such other admin., financial, technical and organizational arrangements | Due Date :23-May-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IIB4 | Description :The Recipient shall install, within the PCU, a customized multi-sitesaccounting software in a manner satisfactory to the Association - Not later than four (4) months after Effective date | Due Date:24-Jul-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IIB5 | Description :The Recipient shall recruit an internal auditor with qualifications,experience and terms of reference acceptable to the Association - Not later than four (4) months after Effective date | Due Date:24-Jul-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section IIB6 | Description :The Recipient shall recruit an external auditor with qualifications,experience and terms of reference acceptable to the Association - Not later than four (4) months after Effective date | Due Date:24-Jul-2014
